videos.description: After a slow start for both teams, Daniel Batcho ties the game for Texas Tech with the big slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Daniel Batcho gets open under the basket for a Texas Tech dunk) 2021/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Daniel Batcho gets open under the basket for a Texas Tech dunk

videos.description: Jordan O'Neal goes strong to the basket but gets rejected by Chibuzo Agbo who gets the ball back for Texas Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Agbo stuffs O’Neal under the hoop) 2021/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Agbo stuffs O'Neal under the hoop

videos.description: Davion Warren steals the ball and breaks away for a huge slam dunk keeping Texas Tech in the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Steal to sledge hammer dunk for Warren) 2021/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Steal to sledge hammer dunk for Warren

videos.description: Texas Tech applies pressure causing Alabama State to loose the ball as Adonis Arms finishes with a wide open slam dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Texas Tech steals ball for huge slam dunk) 2021/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas Tech steals ball for huge slam dunk

videos.description: Adonis Arms takes no mercy as he flushes another huge dunk against Alabama State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Adonis Arms finishes half with two-handed dunk) 2021/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Adonis Arms finishes half with two-handed dunk

videos.description: Clarence Nadolny pivots to find Adonis Arms who thunders to the basket for a clean dunk.

videos.headline: Nadolny connects with Arms for the dunk

videos.description: Adonis Arms takes the ball away from Alabama State and finishes with an easy dunk.

videos.description: After a slow start for both teams, No. 25 Texas Tech comes out victorious over Alabama State.
